Olakunle Churchill, the ex-husband of actress Tonto Dikeh has broken his silence hours after the actress took to her social media page to reveal the real reason why she left her marriage. Tonto alleged that she quit her marriage after finding out that her husband sleeps with men. Hours after the damaging claim, Churchill posted a message on his Instastories stating that her efforts to drag him down after 4 years will not work. See post below: Source